  "remarks": "QDe.148. Established by foreign terrorist fighters in 2013. Location: Syrian Arab Republic. Affiliated with Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115) and AI-Nusrah Front for the People of the Levant (QDe.137). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 6 Aug. 2015 ( amended on 24 Nov. 2020 )",
